Text0_0_loc8='Greetings, $C. For some, the hunter is a way of life, a chosen profession. For others, it is something of a pastime, a badge of courage, or a rite of passage depending on your tribe.$B$BFor me, race and profession mean nothing--it is the testing of your spirit and mind that I respect. For one to stand against the forces of nature and test all of their skills is the true mark of honor.$B$BIf you wish to test yourself and earn my respect, then speak to me more.'
Text0_0_loc8='I can get back to the Stronghold on my own -- I just need a hand getting the blazes out of this hive!$B$BWho... who are you?'
