Text0_0_loc8='This windblossom plant stands out as a beacon of light in the darkness that is Felwood.  Plump and juicy berries hang from the plant, ripe for the picking.'
Text0_0_loc8='This healthy whipper root plant stands as a polar opposite to the sickly taint of corruption that dominates Felwood.  Tender and healthy roots yield delicious tubers that lay on the ground next to the plant.'
Text0_0_loc8='This vibrant night dragon plant stands in stark contrast to the demonic taint that sunders Felwood.  Rare and luscious fruit, known as Night Dragon\'s Breath, hang heavily from the plant.'
