Text0_0_loc8='Right then... You have to build an arcanite buoy and place it in the ocean. My minnow will be attracted to the magical emanations. When he gets near the buoy - BLAMMO! It will explode in a glorious pulse of arcane energy, revealing the minnow\'s true form. Also, you may or may not incur the wrath of Neptulon. A 50/50 chance I would say.'
