Text0_0_loc8='Take this ledger to an old acquaintance of mine in Tanaris. His name is Narain Soothfancy - terrible, terrible psychic but an amazing engineer! He should be able to make sense of it all.
$B$B
No need to thank me, $N. It\'s the least I could do.$B$B
Good day!'
