Text0_0_loc8='Hello, $N. What can I do for you?',Text0_1_loc8='Hello, $N. What can I do for you?'
Text0_0_loc8='You must be hard up to be wandering these Badlands, $C. Hard up like me.$B$BOr maybe you\'re here because you\'re crazy. Crazy, like me.'
Text0_0_loc8='In order to serve the Dark Lady and Varimathras we need to advance the front on the Human Infestation.'
Text0_0_loc8='We are but so close to developing the New Plague that our Dark Lady desires with such fervor.'
Text0_0_loc8='Thanks to the Warchief, even here in the remains of our former prison, some hope remains, and the Horde rises anew.'
